high_descs: Turn to your right and go to the white table on your left.
Pick up the fork on the table, between the two, gold wine glasses on the table.
Place the fork inside the first wine glass, closest to the edge of the table.
Pick up the wine glass with the fork inside it.
Turn to your right and go to the sink, then move over to the counter to the right of the sink.
Place the wine glass with the fork inside it, on the counter to the right of the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a wine glass, containing a fork on the counter.

high_descs: Turn right and go forward, then turn left at the white table.
Pick up the fork on the white table.
Put the fork in the cup nearest to you.
Pick up the cup with the fork in it.
Turn around go to the white table behind you, then turn left to go to the counter.
Put the cup on the counter.
anns.task_desc: Put a cup with a fork in it on the counter.

high_descs: Turn right, move the the white table on the left, turn left to face the cups on the table.
Pick up the fork on the table.
Put the fork in the orange cup closer to you on the table.
Pick up the cup with fork on the table.
Turn around, bring the cup over the the lettuce on the counter to the left.
Put the cup on the counter, left of the lettuce.
anns.task_desc: Put a cup with fork in it on the counter.
